import numpy as np

def score(item: int, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    remaining_capacity = bins - item
    max_remaining_capacity = np.max(bins)
    bin_indices = np.arange(1, len(bins) + 1)

    scores = (
        np.exp(-(remaining_capacity / max_remaining_capacity) ** bin_indices)
        + np.sqrt(remaining_capacity)
        + np.log(remaining_capacity)
    )

    sorted_indices = np.argsort(scores)[::-1]
    scores = scores[sorted_indices]

    return scores
